HEADWORD: Unpolled
<hw>Un*polled"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not polled.</def>
Specifically: <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Not enumerated or registered; <as>as, an
<ex>unpolled</ex> vote or voter</as>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Not
plundered.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unpoll'd</xex> Arabian
wealth.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Fanshawe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

